Package: pbcharts
Title: Process Behaviour Charts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jacob", "Anh√∏j", , "jacob@anhoej.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: `pbcharts` draws run charts and individuals control charts for
  count and measurement data. The control limits in individual charts adjust
  to varying subgroup sizes if a denominator is present as suggested by Taylor (2017)
  <https://variation.com/normalized-individuals-control-chart/>.
URL: https://github.com/anhoej/pbcharts
